<p>Finding what&#39;s using your free space, sorting out multi-monitor setups with Thunderbolt, long-term SSD reliability confusion and adding more USB ports to your Mac are just a few of the topics that Dave and John cover in this week&#39;s episode of Mac Geek Gab. Download, press play and enjoy!</p>
